The paper deals with tracking multiple targets, which is a common problem in computer vision and robotics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves the use of a Gaussian mixture and a state estimator, which are common techniques in control theory and machine learning. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories.
